sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant W as Worker Consumer
  participant DB as Postgres
  participant R as Retry Loop
  participant K as Redpanda/Kafka
  participant D as DLQ Topic
  participant Ops as Operator

  W->>DB: upsert InboxEvent(PENDING)
  W->>DB: processOrderConfirmed()
  DB-->>W: error (e.g., order not found)
  W-->>DB: keep InboxEvent PENDING (will retry)

  loop until success or max attempts
    R->>DB: select PENDING where availableAt<=now
    R->>DB: processOrderConfirmed()
    alt success
      R->>DB: mark PROCESSED
    else fail
      R->>DB: attempts++ , availableAt=now+backoff
    end
  end

  alt max attempts reached
    R->>DB: mark FAILED + lastError
    R->>K: produce to DLQ
    K->>D: DLQ message stored
  end

  Ops->>DB: replay CLI sets FAILED->PENDING (availableAt=now)
  R->>DB: reprocess
